:::Jetstorm/Godfather:::

::the battle drives jetstorm insane.  he turns to Godfather::
Jetstorm: Dammit! I can't take this!
Godfather: Hey, hey, don't go pulling a mini-mafia on me!
Jetstorm: Give me your pistol.
Godfather: Oh, no.  You are NOT going to blow your brains out when im around.
Jetstorm: Oh yes it will!
::he grabs Godfather's gun and shoots himself 5 times in the head. His head 
falls off::
Godfather: For Primus' sake!  Why is everyone dying lately?!
::He finds Shockaract::
Godfather: Hey, boss, Jetstorm just killed himself.

--part1_42.14879c34.282e0ff8_boundary
